query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('alpha',
'amazon-route53',
'django-class-based-views',
'fixed',
'glm',
'kineticjs',
'member',
'scikit-image',
'smack',
'state-machine',
'tar',
'tfs2015',
'word',
'xul');
